{'hash': 'f2cf6a63f98401ac9c4d79c9385b2c277d1fb20f', 'query': 'SELECT T1.artistID, COUNT(T2.paintingID), COUNT(T3.sculptureID) FROM Artists AS T1 JOIN Paintings AS T2 ON T1.artistID = T2.painterID JOIN Sculptures AS T3 ON T1.artistID = T3.sculptorID WHERE T2.title != T3.title LIMIT 10', 'template': 'SELECT #COLUMN#, COUNT(#COLUMN#), COUNT(#COLUMN#) FROM #TABLE# JOIN #TABLE# ON #COLUMN# = #COLUMN# JOIN #TABLE# ON #COLUMN# = #COLUMN# WHERE #COLUMN# != #COLUMN# LIMIT #VALUE#'}
